description: This Chainlink VRF hall of fame Sakura purrs with a rating of 98, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 98, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 5 for East, 3 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/10981-65390-0.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Sakura [98 Votes, Hall of Fame]
